OL,3,CWhat are my rights when a flight is
OL,4,Cdelayed?
OL,6,FPassengers who suffer flight
OL,7,Fdisruption are often left unsure what
OL,8,Fthey are entitled to.
OL,10,FHere the PA news agency answers 13 key
OL,11,Fquestions on assistance and
OL,12,Fcompensation.
OL,14,F` What flights are covered by UK
OL,15,Fconsumer law?
