OL,3,CWhat are my rights when a flight is
OL,4,Cdelayed?
OL,6,FFlights operated by an airline
OL,7,Fdeparting from a UK airport, flights
OL,8,Foperated by a UK or EU airline
OL,9,Farriving at a UK airport, or flights
OL,10,Foperated by a UK airline arriving at
OL,11,Fan EU airport.
OL,13,F` How long must a flight be delayed
OL,14,Fbefore I am entitled to assistance?
OL,16,FIt depends on the distance of the
OL,17,Fflight.
OL,19,FFor flights under 1,500km (932 miles)
OL,20,Fsuch as from Glasgow to Amsterdam: at
OL,21,Fleast two hours.
