OL,3,CWhat are my rights when a flight is
OL,4,Cdelayed?
OL,6,FFor flights between 1,500km (932
OL,7,Fmiles) and 3,500km (2,175 miles) such
OL,8,Fas from Manchester to Marrakesh: at
OL,9,Fleast three hours.
OL,11,FFor flights over 3,500km (2,175 miles)
OL,12,Fsuch as from Heathrow to New York: at
OL,13,Fleast four hours.
