OL,3,CWhat are my rights when a flight is
OL,4,Cdelayed?
OL,6,FThe Civil Aviation Authority (CAA)
OL,7,Fsays in this scenario, passengers can
OL,8,Forganise their own assistance and
OL,9,Fclaim the costs back from the airline
OL,10,Fby submitting receipts.
OL,12,F` Does that mean I should book a
OL,13,Fluxury hotel suite and order champagne?
OL,15,FAirlines are unlikely to reimburse you
OL,16,Ffor that. The CAA advises passengers
OL,17,Fnot to "spend more than is reasonable".
