OL,3,CWhat are my rights when a flight is
OL,4,Cdelayed?
OL,6,FUntil your flight takes off or you
OL,7,Faccept a refund after deciding not to
OL,8,Ftravel.
OL,10,F` What about getting to my destination?
OL,12,FIf a flight is cancelled, airlines are
OL,13,Frequired to get you to your
OL,14,Fdestination if you still want to
OL,15,Ftravel.
