OL,3,CWhat are my rights when a flight is
OL,4,Cdelayed?
OL,6,FMost will book you onto another of
OL,7,Ftheir flights, but you may be entitled
OL,8,Fto travel with another airline or by
OL,9,Fan alternative mode of transport if it
OL,10,Fwill get you to your destination
OL,11,Fsignificantly sooner.
OL,13,FPassengers doing this are often
OL,14,Frequired to purchase their own tickets
OL,15,Fand submit a claim to their original
OL,16,Fairline for reimbursement.
OL,18,F` What if I no longer want to travel?
