OL,3,CWhat are my rights when a flight is
OL,4,Cdelayed?
OL,6,FYou are entitled to a refund if you
OL,7,Fhave been delayed by more than five
OL,8,Fhours.
OL,10,F` Am I entitled to compensation for a
OL,11,Fdelayed flight?
OL,13,FAirlines may be liable for
OL,14,Fcompensation if the reason for a delay
OL,15,Fis deemed within their control, such
OL,16,Fas a fault with the aircraft or pilot
OL,17,Fsickness.
