OL,3,CWhat are my rights when a flight is
OL,4,Cdelayed?
OL,6,FCauses of disruption classed as
OL,7,Foutside their control include severe
OL,8,Fweather, air traffic control
OL,9,Frestrictions and security alerts.
OL,11,F` How much can I claim for a delay?
OL,13,FIt depends on the length of the flight
OL,14,Fand how much its arrival was later
OL,15,Fthan scheduled.
OL,17,FFor flights under 1,500km (932 miles):
OL,18,F#220 for a delay of at least three
OL,19,Fhours.
