OL,3,CWhat are my rights when a flight is
OL,4,Cdelayed?
OL,6,FYou are entitled to a refund or a
OL,7,Freplacement flight, and the same
OL,8,Fassistance as if your flight was
OL,9,Fdelayed.
OL,11,F` Can I claim compensation if my
OL,12,Fflight is cancelled?
OL,14,FYou can if the reason is deemed within
OL,15,Fthe airline's control, you received no
OL,16,Fmore than 14 days' notice, and
OL,17,Fdepending on the timings of a new
OL,18,Fflight offered.
